    "name": "Adaptory",
    "steam_appid": 2201620,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当坠落在未知太空深处一颗荒芜的行星上后，你的任务是让你的四名探险家船员存活得足够长的时间，以便找到回家的路。Adaptory 结合了以物理为基础的深度模拟与基础建设和探索。随着你的团队深入地表，人际关系会不断发展，挑战也会不断出现，重建飞船的重要性最终可能会让位于揭开这块看似死寂的岩石的神秘面纱。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201620/extras/7e533255b32a3598c2027da533511c2e.avif?t=1772059355\" width=616 height=100 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个船员都是一个独特的个体，在每个游戏开始时按程序生成。你的目标是让它们活着：呼吸、进食、温暖、健康和快乐。每个探险家都拥有自己的技能、特点和观点，他们会毫不犹豫地与其他船员分享。他们的对话与日记是故事和游戏不可或缺的一部分，有助于你找出如何在充满挑战的环境中最有效地利用他们的技能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201620/extras/3139f90bb83f0b0e6e97d1e42d98702b.poster.avif?t=1772059355\" width=780 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201620/extras/3139f90bb83f0b0e6e97d1e42d98702b.webm?t=1772059355\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201620/extras/3139f90bb83f0b0e6e97d1e42d98702b.mp4?t=1772059355\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201620/extras/f84fd9210da64dae5d6b0946bd5ccea9.avif?t=1772059355\" width=616 height=100 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >坠毁的飞船可以提供庇护并能让你的船员生存一段时间。但为了生存，你必须建设一个适合的基地并组建一个能够面对任何危险的灵活社区。你的船员需要一个可以睡觉、进食、洗漱、治疗和闲逛的地方以保持士气。管理温度、连接、管道——这仅仅是个开始。复杂性会随着时间的推移而提高。最终，你必须实现基地自动化，因为基地在发展，您的任务清单也在发展，但你的团队规模却不会发展。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201620/extras/d96968829376ecec31efc859c4034068.poster.avif?t=1772059355\" width=780 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201620/extras/d96968829376ecec31efc859c4034068.webm?t=1772059355\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201620/extras/d96968829376ecec31efc859c4034068.mp4?t=1772059355\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201620/extras/83061e5dff6a7e82b69ae190ea9bbcdb.avif?t=1772059355\" width=616 height=100 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Adaptory 在复杂的物理和化学系统上运行，模拟重力、温度、密度、粘度，甚至相变，拥有接近五十种不同的材料可供学习和实验。利用他们为你谋利。需要能源吗？安装太阳能电池板阵列以捕捉阳光。或者用熔岩沸水发电，产生蒸汽或将天然气输送到涡轮机。但请记住：每场游戏都是全新的、按程序生成的体验，都拥有独特的挑战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201620/extras/793eaf88f5dbfce44150a6402652ac95.poster.avif?t=1772059355\" width=780 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201620/extras/793eaf88f5dbfce44150a6402652ac95.webm?t=1772059355\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201620/extras/793eaf88f5dbfce44150a6402652ac95.mp4?t=1772059355\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201620/extras/c5347f6228934a143f56b3eee36c5827.avif?t=1772059355\" width=616 height=100 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每场比赛都会出现意想不到的波折。随机出现的流星雨、太阳耀斑和地震都可能会破坏你的基地，但也会提供意想不到的机遇，比如获得稀有材料或发掘新的矿脉和文物，只要你的探险家们能够在这些事件中幸存下来。即使你的基地没有出现任何问题，也可能会使你的一名船员陷入崩溃的边缘，或者导致关系破裂。你将会何去何从？你会？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201620/extras/7e031fa90a6a0d6188bc76fd91b594e4.poster.avif?t=1772059355\" width=780 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201620/extras/7e031fa90a6a0d6188bc76fd91b594e4.webm?t=1772059355\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201620/extras/7e031fa90a6a0d6188bc76fd91b594e4.mp4?t=1772059355\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201620/extras/76f0615ad616db3a6c6b5dc755f0b286.avif?t=1772059355\" width=616 height=100 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Adaptory 是一个独立的故事，故事背景设定在一个更宏伟的宇宙中。你将能够通过船员的日记、可能在小行星深处找到的文物、系统日志甚至随机对话来一探究竟。从你的船员母星的历史和他们的深空任务，到实际发生的神秘事件，拼凑出一个由获奖作家 Cassandra Tse 所创作的扣人心弦的科幻故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201620/extras/f6db4066df02836c4ea7f8850d9ed7d6.poster.avif?t=1772059355\" width=780 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201620/extras/f6db4066df02836c4ea7f8850d9ed7d6.webm?t=1772059355\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2201620/extras/f6db4066df02836c4ea7f8850d9ed7d6.mp4?t=1772059355\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Adaptory 是一款雄心壮志的游戏，结合了基地建设、现实模拟、突发游戏、角色发展和随机生成的事件，随着版本 1.0 的来临，我们正在积极开发并定期更新。我们将根据您的反馈推出新的系统和机制，因此请加入 Adaptory Discord 以获取早期版本并加入社区！</p>",
